Program: Outlook
Title: A Teacher Student Reunion
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsj5
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The story of Cassius who speaks to his former school teacher for the first time in 40 years. Also, a project in Calcutta to send children born in prisons to top city schools. Peter White and the migrant worker separated from her family in China. Finally, mud cakes in Haiti.